{
  "texts": [
    "However, the spectral shapes of the predicted GW spectra are generally different, which can help to disentangle between different types of backgrounds.",
    "In this work, we focus on four possible scenarios:",
    "An inflationary GWB from the amplification of quantum fluctuations of the gravitational field, 2.",
    "A GWB from a network of cosmic string loops, 3.",
    "A GWB from vortical (M)HD turbulence at the QCD energy scale, A94, page 13 of 30 4."
  ]
}